trans-unit.source: Represents the configuration settings of a language provider.
trans-unit.target: Representerer konfigurasjonsinnstillingene for en språk-leverandør.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the configured <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Henter typen for den konfigurerte <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> implementering.

trans-unit.source: The machine configuration file contains the fully qualified type name for each <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Maskinen konfigurasjonsfilen inneholder fullstendige Typenavnet for hver <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering på datamaskinen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: The CodeDomProviderType property value is a <xref:System.Type> instance that represents a configured language provider implementation.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien CodeDomProviderType er en <xref:System.Type>-forekomst som representerer en konfigurerte språket leverandøren implementering.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref:System.Type> instance that represents the configured language provider type.
trans-unit.target: En skrivebeskyttet <xref:System.Type>-forekomst som representerer konfigurerte språket leverandørtypen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The language provider is not configured on this computer.
trans-unit.target: Språkleverandøren er ikke konfigurert på denne datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Cannot locate the type because it is a <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or empty string.
trans-unit.target: Finner ikke typen fordi den er en <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller tom streng.

trans-unit.source: -or- Cannot locate the type because the name for the <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> cannot be found in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: - eller - finner ikke typen fordi navnet på den <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> finnes ikke i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the configured compiler settings for the language provider implementation.
trans-unit.target: Henter innstillingene for konfigurerte kompilatoren for språket leverandøren implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters"></xref> instance that contains the compiler options and settings configured for the language provider.
trans-unit.target: En skrivebeskyttet <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters"> </xref> -forekomst som inneholder kompilatoren alternativer og innstillinger som er konfigurert for språkleverandøren.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> instance for the current language provider settings.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> forekomsten for gjeldende Språkinnstillinger for leverandøren.

trans-unit.source: The CreateProvider method returns a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> instance for the current language provider settings.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateProvider returnerer en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>-forekomst for gjeldende Språkinnstillinger for leverandøren.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: Use the CreateProvider method to get a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation for a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo> instance returned by the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Bruke CreateProvider metode for å få en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering for en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo>forekomsten ble returnert av den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: A CodeDOM provider associated with the language provider configuration.
trans-unit.target: En CodeDOM leverandør som er forbundet med språket Leverandørkonfigurasjon.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> instance for the current language provider settings and specified options.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> forekomsten for gjeldende språkinnstillinger leverandør og angitte alternativene.

trans-unit.source: The CreateProvider method returns a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> instance for the current language provider settings and the specified provider options.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateProvider returnerer en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>-forekomst for gjeldende språkinnstillingene for leverandøren og alternativene angitt leverandør.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: For information about supported provider options, see the specific CodeDOM provider documentation.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om alternativer for støttet leverandør, kan du se dokumentasjonen for leverandøren bestemte CodeDOM.

trans-unit.source: Use the CreateProvider method to get a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation for a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo> instance returned by the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Bruke CreateProvider metode for å få en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering for en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo>forekomsten ble returnert av den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetAllCompilerInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: A collection of provider options from the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: En samling av leverandøralternativer i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: A CodeDOM provider associated with the language provider configuration and specified options.
trans-unit.target: En CodeDOM-leverandør som er forbundet med språket Leverandørkonfigurasjon og angitt alternativer.

trans-unit.source: providerOptions is .
trans-unit.target: providerOptions is .

trans-unit.source: The provider does not support options.
trans-unit.target: Leverandøren støtter ikke alternativer.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object represents the same language provider and compiler settings as the current <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om det angitte objektet representerer samme leverandør og kompilatoren språkinnstillingene som gjeldende <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides the <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer den <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The two instances are considered equal if the values of the following properties are equal: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: To forekomster regnes lik hvis verdiene i de følgende egenskapene er like: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A>, and <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A> properties of the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters> instance returned by the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateDefaultCompilerParameters%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A>, Og <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A>egenskapene for den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters>forekomsten ble returnert av den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateDefaultCompilerParameters%2A>metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateDefaultCompilerParameters%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A>

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with the current <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som skal sammenlignes med gjeldende <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: if o is a object and its value is the same as this instance; otherwise, .
trans-unit.target: Hvis o er en objekt og verdien er den samme som denne forekomsten; ellers .

trans-unit.source: Returns the file name extensions supported by the language provider.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer filen filtypene som støttes av språkleverandøren.

trans-unit.source: The [\<system.codedom\> Element](../Topic/%3Csystem.codedom%3E%20Element.md) in the machine configuration file contains the language provider and compiler configuration settings for each <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Den [ \<system.codedom\> Elementet](../Topic/%3Csystem.codedom%3E%20Element.md) i maskinkonfigurasjonen av filen inneholder språket leverandør og kompilatoren konfigurasjonsinnstillingene for hver <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering på datamaskinen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: Each configured language provider supports one or more file name extensions.
trans-unit.target: Hver konfigurerte språkleverandøren støtter én eller flere filtyper.

trans-unit.source: For example, a <xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName> might support the file name extensions ".cs" and ".c#".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en <xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName>støtter kanskje filen navnet utvidelser ".cs" og ".c #".</xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An array of file name extensions supported by the language provider.
trans-unit.target: En matrise med filtyper støttes av språkleverandøren.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer hashkoden for den gjeldende forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides the <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer den <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This method generates the same hash code for two objects that are equal according to the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.Equals%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, samme hash-kode for de to objektene som er lik i henhold til den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.Equals%2A>metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.Equals%2A>

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer hash code for the current <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"></xref> instance, suitable for use in hashing algorithms and data structures such as a hash table.
trans-unit.target: En 32-biters heltall med fortegn hash-kode for gjeldende <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo"> </xref> forekomsten passer for bruk i nummer algoritmer og data strukturer som en hash-tabell.

trans-unit.source: Gets the language names supported by the language provider.
trans-unit.target: Henter språknavn som støttes av språkleverandøren.

trans-unit.source: The [\<system.codedom\> Element](../Topic/%3Csystem.codedom%3E%20Element.md) in the machine configuration file contains the language provider and compiler configuration settings for each <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Den [ \<system.codedom\> Elementet](../Topic/%3Csystem.codedom%3E%20Element.md) i maskinkonfigurasjonen av filen inneholder språket leverandør og kompilatoren konfigurasjonsinnstillingene for hver <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering på datamaskinen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: Each configured language provider supports one or more language names.
trans-unit.target: Hver konfigurerte språkleverandøren støtter én eller flere språknavn.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo> object for a <xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName> might return an array with the language names "c#", "cs", and "csharp".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo>objekt en <xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName>kan returnerer en matrise med språket navn "c#", "cs" og "c Sharp".</xref:Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo>

trans-unit.source: An array of language names supported by the language provider.
trans-unit.target: En rekke språknavn som støttes av språkleverandøren.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the language provider implementation is configured on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om språket leverandøren implementeringen er konfigurert på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Use the IsCodeDomProviderTypeValid property to check the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation before accessing the provider properties or methods.
trans-unit.target: Bruk IsCodeDomProviderTypeValid-egenskapen for å se den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering før tilgang til Leverandøregenskaper og metoder.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: For example, after you get the language provider settings from the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A> method, use the IsCodeDomProviderTypeValid property to verify the provider type implementation before calling the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateProvider%2A> method or using the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når du får språket leverandørinnstillingene fra den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A>metoden, bruke egenskapen IsCodeDomProviderTypeValid til å bekrefte implementering av typen leverandør før du kaller den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateProvider%2A>metoden eller bruker den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CodeDomProviderType%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerInfo.CreateProvider%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.GetCompilerInfo%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the language provider implementation type is configured on the computer; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis Implementeringstypen språket leverandøren er konfigurert på datamaskinen. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
